<bibRefCitation author="Bartsch, I." box="[1003,1169,979,1005]" pageId="4" pageNumber="305" pagination="27 - 31" refId="ref8320" refString="Bartsch, I. (1984 a) Two new species of the pulcher group in the genus Copidognathus (Acari, Halacaridae). Zoologica Scripta, 13, 27 - 31. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1463 - 6409.1984. tb 00019. x" type="journal article" year="1984">Bartsch 1984a</bibRefCitation>
